ic.codemao.cn/FpAat_azqJbAbioZpWRqO8pMTg65\"><br></p>\n<p>好，然后再编写代码：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fqo7k-FF3Kl8R6nzySNe6HxN2gnk\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FjtFmBcHjB9SCMGkj2cDtgEzmF3J\"><br></p>\n<p>好，还有最后一步。进入编程猫格式工厂把这个作品转换成EXE模式，就OK。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<font size=\"7\" color=\"#ffcc00\">-End-</font></p>\n<p><br></p>","board_id":"2","board_name":"积木编程乐园","updated_at":1518348305,"created_at":1518252195,"n_views":222,"n_replies":52,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}